- not_now_polite (polite decline, maybe later, timing issue, too busy right now)
- not_interested (firm no, not relevant to them, wrong person)
- unsubscribe (asks to be removed, stop contacting, do not contact again)
- neutral (unclear intent, just acknowledging receipt, asking questions)

Respond with ONLY the classification label, nothing else."
    }]
  }],
  "generationConfig": {
    "temperature": 0.1,
    "maxOutputTokens": 50
  }
}

